name: '91 Series No. 1A
description: Original work by SSIM. The Series includes still images of the ’91 Series No 1 (One of One) on Ethereum’s ERC-721. These minted on Hicetnunc & are numbered 1A, 1B & 1C. Edition Numbered to 25. This is an abstract view of a vision from a painter from the 20th century (Year 1900-2000) would express his imagination on the future of space travel would be like in the 3rd millennium (Year 2001-3000) - To see more: www.ssimartist.com / @ssimartist
